Celebrating progress. Actor @regejean, is inspired by people who have a story to be told. Progress to him means changing storytelling by making it broader, more diverse, and accessible to everyone. Honoring a new direction and our ability to grow, adapt and change.

go.audi/rjp-progress

#Audi #Q4etron #FutureIsAnAttitude #emobility
--------------------
